2.0 (changes from the base mod)

- tame chance formula expanded — now accounts for target's injuries, stun, taunt, and low morale, and scales with player level (double at level 11)
- tame chance shown in combat log
- fixed crash on loading corrupted save
- Russian localization (needs Rosetta)

Compatibility:

- creature identified by class now:
    - makes things work with translated game
    - generally more mod and future compatible
- work with Northern Expansion direwolf
- avoid conflicts with Nested Tooltips mod
- double tame chance for the Proper Druid / XBE druid background
